\id MAT Gugu Yimidhirr selection 21:1-9 
\h Matthew 
\toc1 Matthew 
\toc2 Matthew 
\toc3 MAT 
\mt1 Matthew  
\c 21
\p
\v 1 Tana jubaiko Jerusalem kadai je mon Bethphage jubaiko milnkol mantjal Jesus nulu kortiva jerkangāi nangu tegai  
\v 2 nulu koko jerba damangan: “Jubale date jambanai, jura natinujina jemon, jubale mamalma jereman kadeiga kankaltjir gumbin darngal, jina ngato mante.  
\v 3 Bama jendu koko batal; ngani? jubale jerba: ‘Master ngantanan tegai’, ujurke nulu tana tegala.”  
\v 4 Jinarana jitaranu, koko propetawai manuputan merilil, nulu jerba:   
\q1
\v 5 “Nudi koko batala ngutur Sion:  
\q1 Namala master nganu kada nganunka,  
\q2 dauun ningankal dagarkar jeremantjir.”   
\m
\v 6 Nangu jerkangai datai m balkalkai, wandare Jesus koko banti danangan.  
\v 7 Tana mante jereman kankaltjir marar tanangan pirbai dagargar m jitare nangu jemon.  
\v 8 Bama warkangamu dambare marar tanangan dutanwai mundal jokungan pinda bantila m najun dutanwai dambare.  
\v 9 Bama warkangamu gurir datai m dagalbai. Kadai ganal bantil jerba:  
\q1 “Hosianna jumur David,  
\q2 nundu kadai puriwai masterngan,  
\q1 Hosianna wankarwai.”   